  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Identifying Indonesian Translations**\n\nI\'m currently focused on identifying the text strings within `/src/App.tsx` that require Indonesian translation. Specifically, I\'ve found the first phrase: \"Are you sure you wish to delete this cardiac record?\" which needs to be rendered as \"Apakah Anda yakin ingin menghapus catatan medis kardiak ini?\". I\'m now looking for additional strings.\n\n\n**Expanding Indonesian Translations**\n\nI\'ve translated a few more phrases within the codebase. The warning about wiping custom data is now \"Tindakan ini akan menghapus semua data khusus dan mengembalikan 6 catatan medis bawaan dari dataset Kaggle. Lanjutkan?\". Additionally, the database history clearing prompt is translated. I\'ve also addressed the \"no records to export\" alert, and localized the system sync label and app description, and confirmed we do not need to change the main app title.\n\n\n**Localizing Interface Labels**\n\nI\'ve been working to localize more interface labels. I just translated \"Database Status: {records.length} records\" to \"Status Database: {records.length} rekam medis.\" I\'ve also localized the application banner text, translating \"Kaggle Clinical Dataset Aligned\" to \"Kesesuaian Dataset Klinis Kaggle,\" \"Heart Failure Predictive Analysis & Diagnostics\" to \"Analisis Prediktif & Diagnostik Gagal Jantung,\" and the longer descriptive text to the Indonesian equivalent. Finally, I\'ve started the localization of the tab labels.\n\n\n**Translating More UI Elements**\n\nI\'ve translated more UI elements now. I\'ve localized \"Database Records ({records.length})\" to \"Riwayat Rekam Medis ({records.length})\". Then, for the quick buttons, I translated \"Export Database (CSV)\" to \"Ekspor Database (CSV)\", \"Reset Defaults\" to \"Atur Ulang Default\", and \"Reset Database to Pristine Kaggle Demo Records\" to \"Atur Ulang Database ke Rekam Medis Demo Kaggle Asli\". Additionally, I\'ve started the database page. I\'ve rendered translations of: \"Patient Diagnostic History Logs\" as \"Riwayat Catatan Diagnostik Pasien\", the descriptive text, and a number of filter labels. I\'ve translated all risk labels.\n\n\n**Localizing Table and Risk**\n\nI\'ve just finished localizing more strings. The \"Critical Risk\" label is now \"Risiko Kritis\". I translated the \"No Patient Records Match Your Parameter\" and the follow-up text. I\'ve translated all the table headers, and have localized some of the strings in the table body as well. I also localized a glucose-related label.\n\n\n**Refining Table and Footer**\n\nI\'ve made progress on translating more parts of the table. I\'ve localized some glucose-related labels and standardized a display. I translated \'Gula Darah Normal\'. I am also working on the risk levels. I\'ve started the localization for the footer, and I\'ve started translating `Delete this record` to `Hapus catatan ini`.\n\n\n**Refining Textual Descriptions**\n\nI\'ve just finished the complete localization of the informational text, translating the description of CardioSphere AI and the copyright and telemetry notice. The initial block translations were straightforward and I\'ve verified that the output looks good. I\'m now setting up a few more translation blocks.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will modify the first portion of `/src/App.tsx` (lines 60 to 121) to translate modal confirmations and warning messages into Indonesian."
